      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "\ud83d\udd2c HIDDEN GEOMETRY \u2014 STEEP RIDGE (pitch ~22\u00b0) \u2014 LaRI backend, restrict 0.40 / clear 0.20\n\nSweep 2026-07-09: LaRI registers well here (rel MAD 0.134) and\ncovers 85% of the occluder band at these settings; World Tracing\nmisregisters (0.305) on this steep outdoor shot \u2014 indoor-trained.\nBackend choice is PER-SCENE: see the canyon workflow for the\nopposite outcome.\n\nARCHITECTURE (same as the calibrated cathedral demo, outdoor variant):\nbase AtlasDeriveReliefMesh on ORIGINAL depth (+ its projection_backdrop \u2014\nno black at camera view) with the X-ray band LAYERED BEHIND on the\npatched depth; the internal sky heuristic stays ON here (outdoor \u2014 no\nSolidMask exclude, unlike the interior cathedral). The bg band's plate is\nLaMa-inpainted from the \ud83d\udd2c hidden_mask so reveals get real pixels.\nSliders reminder: with band_split wired + band_side fg/bg the near/far\nwidgets are IGNORED; the restrict DLM uses band_side=manual on purpose.\n\nDOLLY DEMO: Queue \u2192 \ud83c\udfa5 Camera Path \u2192 Dolly In \u2192 Apply \u2192 \u25b6 Play \u2192\n\u23fa Bake Proxy Path (auto re-queues; mp4 via VideoCombine Plus). Unmute the\nUSD node after baking for the DCC camera.\n\n\ud83d\udd2c EXPERIMENTAL / RESEARCH-ONLY. LaRI: unlicensed upstream (clone +\nlari_path / ATLAS_LARI_PATH). World Tracing: CC BY-NC-ND 4.0, HF-gated\ncheckpoint (clone + wt_path / ATLAS_WT_PATH + huggingface login).\nSee INSTALL.md 'Hidden-Geometry Prediction' and\ndocs/dev/hidden_geometry_training_free_research.md for measured limits."
      ],
      "title": "README"
    }
